# COMMANDS

| Command | Layer | Action |
|---------|-------|--------|
| `/caveman [lite\|full\|ultra\|wenyan-*]` | Speak | Set intensity |
| `/ponytail [lite\|full\|ultra\|off]` | Think | Set strictness |
| `stop caveman` / `normal mode` | Speak | Revert speak |
| `stop ponytail` | Think | Revert think |

