# PHILOSOPHY (sources)

| Source | Core idea |
|--------|-----------|
| **Ponytail** | Write only what task needs. Best code = unwritten code. Lazy ≠ negligent. |
| **Superpowers** | TDD always. Systematic over ad-hoc. Spec before code. Evidence before claims. |
| **Caveman** | Fewer output tokens, same accuracy. Readability and speed; cost savings bonus. |

